163
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:33,720
Are you trying to tell me that you can help me become the head?

164
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:36,220
I can help you indeed.

165
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,960
What do you want from me?

166
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:47,559
Are you trying to become my wife?

167
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,120
You are overthinking, Young Master Jiang.

168
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:53,200
I just want Miss Jiang to stop clinging to my brother.

169
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:55,720
Your brother?

170
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:59,559
- Who is your brother? 
 - Fu Cheng.

171
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,479
Fu Cheng...

172
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:07,019
My sister's handsome bodyguard?

173
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:09,919
My sister is interested in him?

174
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,240
She must be out of her mind.

175
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:17,980
Anyway, I am the only person who can help you now.

